rows.label: tlk70000029_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I did a bit of traveling myself back in
the day. Saw a bit of the world.

rows.label: tlk70000029_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Plentiful lands of lakes and forests,
exotic cities with strange houses
and even stranger food...

rows.label: tlk70000029_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But I hafta say, there's no place quite
like Iira. No big wars or famine or
terrible epidemics here!

rows.label: tlk70000029_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Iirans live in peace and quiet thanks
to our wise and prudent king.

rows.label: tlk70000029_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Past kings might have been brutal
despots, but our king rules with reason
and isn't afraid of change or reform.

rows.label: tlk70000029_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Some folks are critical of a king
with such a progressive outlook, but
I think he's clever. Very clever.
